## Next Steps for Production Use
To enable analytics data collection on Vercel:
1. Deploy the project to Vercel (if not already deployed)
2. Navigate to project's Analytics section in Vercel Dashboard
3. Click the "Enable" button to activate analytics
4. Analytics routes will be automatically added at `/_vercel/insights/*`
5. Data collection will begin immediately after enabling

